                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7311" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0224</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10811 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部人控制抑或内部控制重大缺陷？——瑞幸从新星变流星的闪落之谜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insider control or major defects of internal control?  -Luckin&#39;s mystery of changing from a new star to a meteor.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王杏芬，李维斯，何姝濛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞幸咖啡（中国）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务造假；内部人控制；股权制衡；内部控制；重大缺陷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial Fraud; Insider Control; Equity Checks and Balances; Internal Control; Major Defect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年5月，瑞幸咖啡（中国）有限公司（以下简称“瑞幸”）在美国纳斯达克上市，此后一骑绝尘不断扩张，逐步成为资本市场的一颗新星。2020年伊始，浑水发布一则详细的做空报告，剑指瑞幸财务造假蛛丝马迹，随后瑞幸主动自曝，就此跌落神坛。本案例在描述通过瑞幸的“闪落”之路，引导学生从内部人控制（即公司治理失衡）和内部控制重大缺陷（以下简称内控重大缺陷）出发，深入探寻瑞幸内部人凌驾于内部控制之上的原因，并找到完善公司治理和内部控制的最佳途径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> In May 2019, Luckin coffee (China) Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Luckin&quot;) was listed on NASDAQ in the United States, and expanded rapidly, becoming a new star in the capital market. At the beginning of the New Year in 2020, the shorting agency Muddy Waters and Luckin jointly staged a wonderful detective series: from being shorted to taking the initiative to expose, Luckin instantly fell into the world of gods. What is the answer to this &quot;new star&quot; turning into a &quot;meteor&quot;? On the basis of describing the basic situation of the company, this case takes the internal control problem (i.e. the imbalance of corporate governance) and the significant internal control defect (hereinafter referred to as &quot;significant internal control defect&quot;) as the breakthrough point, and guides the students to analyze the specific performance and the deep-seated reasons behind Luckin&#39;s internal control overriding internal control, and make listed companies think more deeply about internal control and internal audit, and explore the best way to establish and improve corporate governance and internal control.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《内部控制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上市公司财务造假原因；内部人控制概念；内部人控制问题成因；内部控制的定义；内部控制八要素；内控重大缺陷的识别；内部人控制问题和内控重大缺陷的关系；股权制衡理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-05</td>
                            </tr>
